":{"id":622910437,"title":"如何评价《斗罗大陆》同人文主角武魂普遍一个比一个逆天的情况？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/622910437","type":"question","created":1695180312,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":28,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18910,89281,208322],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"都说唐三完全是靠武魂优势，可真要自己来写一个比一个逆天，恨不得一出生就无敌，tm连系统都有。而且我寻思唐三在蓝银皇觉醒之前的武魂也就是一个加强版的蓝银草和一个没魂环的昊天锤，不照样把玉天恒和武魂殿黄金一代给锤烂了，战斗过程看起来还算有点悬念，唐家三少后期发电写崩了并不影响前期确实写得还行，到了同人文那基本就是装逼打脸，战斗过程就是一边倒。人品方面就更别说了，唐三那属于初看没觉得有太大问题，事后想想觉得有点不对劲，仔细一看有点逆天，但不管怎么说，他给其他6个人带的仙草是实实在在的，问题的关键在于唐家三少前期说唐门亦正亦邪，后面又变成了唐三冰清玉洁，前后矛盾，而大部分同人文主角的人品真是狗看了都摇头。"},"attached_info":"Cj8InrW0sqzP7Yl5EAMaCTEwMDcwMzgwMSCYzKmoBjAAOBxAC3IJNjIyOTEwNDM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"79 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-06c9ddf08beb46a640f2114aed3e2e91_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1695287750.589189","card_id":"Q_622889166","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":622889166,"title":"如何评价《海贼王》1093话情报？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/622889166","type":"question","created":1695167672,"answer_count":15,"follower_count":16,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[392,161702,163041],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"Cj8InrW0sqzP7Yl5EAMaCTEwMDY5OTA5NiC46aioBjAAOBBADHIJNjIyODg5MTY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"72 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ff6decfd0017d09b4df9e881e10644d1_720w.we